caption.p: GC-MS chemical fingerprint of incense smoke from agarwoods. ( A) Vietnam agarwood. ( B) Liao agarwood. ( C) Cambodian agarwood. Number indicates the compound specifically present in the agarwood. ( D) Venn diagram of 110 compounds identified in the incense smoke from Kynam (K), Vietnam (V), Liao (L), and Cambodian (Ca) agarwoods.
